%section#presentation
  %h2 Presentations materials available
  %p  We have just updated the  #{ link_to 'presentations page', presentations_url }  with a bunch of links to the presentations slides.
  %p  More links and updates are on their way !

  %h2 Welcome to Agile Tour Brussels 2013 !

  %p
    <a href="http://www.atbru.be">Agile Tour Brussels 2013</a> (2nd edition) is an <strong>Agile Conference</strong> that will take place on <strong>September, 27</strong> in <strong>Belgium</strong>:
    %br/
    <a href="http://register.agilesystems.org/">Registration</a> is open and <a herf="http://www.atbru.be/program">Program</a> is available on our website.

  %p At Agile Tour Brussels, there will be both <strong>local</strong> and <strong>international</strong> speakers (U.S, U.K, France, Luxembourg, Italy) coming from various industries like IT, Game Development, Research, Teaching, Marketing...
  %p You will learn and practice themes like <strong>Agile, Scrum, Kanban, XP, Lean, Innovation Games, Agile Games, Systems Thinking, Lean Startup</strong> and also<strong> Problem Solving</strong> and <strong>Soft Skills</strong>.
  %p
    With <strong>30 minute-breaks</strong> between sessions and <strong>lunches</strong>, the Agile Tour Brussels is surely a good place for <strong>Networking</strong>.
    %br/
    Last year we welcomed people from Belgium, France, the Netherlands and Switzerland.
  %h3 Types of sessions
  %p
    During the conference <strong>2 types of sessions</strong> are proposed:
    %br/
    \- <strong>Talks</strong>: A presenter is speaking for most of the time (often from a slide deck), with audience interaction.
    %br/
    \- <strong>Workshops</strong>: Primarily focused on hands-on participation with the audience.
  %h3 For all levels !
  %p
    The <strong>balanced program</strong> offers you the possibility to choose anytime you want a session that could be for <strong>Beginners</strong>, <strong>Practitioners</strong> or <strong>Experts</strong>.

  %h3 Pricing: early birds, normal
  %p You can buy your ticket via the "<a href="http://register.agilesystems.org/">Register</a>" link on top right of this page.
  %p
    \- Until August, 31st 2013, Price is <strong>70EUR</strong> vat excl.
    %br/
    \- After August, 31st 2013, Price is <strong>100EUR</strong> vat excl.

  %h3 See you soon
  %p
    Don't forget to check the <a href="http://www.atbru.be/program">Program</a> and <a href="http://register.agilesystems.org/">Register</a> today !
    %br/
    We hope to see you there !



%section#call
